19256.title: BING Images in AutoCAD
19256.text: Many AutoCAD users wish for orthoimagery or aerial photos within their design drawings.  There are online resources where these can be found paid and for free.  Since AutoCAD version 2014 there has been the ability to overlay Microsoft BING images, right inside AutoCAD!

19241.title: Grading from Alignments
19241.text: Grading cannot be accomplished directly from Civil 3D Alignments.  One can grade only from Feature Lines.  However, a Feature Line can be extracted from an Alignment with an associated profile, either surface profile or design profile.   Sometimes editing elevations is easier using the profile editor and this technique will make that possible.
